Here is the assignment in addition to the first round of interview.

1. Write a shell script to
    I.) Calculate the storage costs of AWS S3 buckets
    II.) Total number of objects
    III.) Total storage size and seggregate them according to storage types
   Assumptions: * The region is us-east-1a
                * aws-cli is not setup to run the script
                * no third-party utilites should be used (example: s3cmd)

2. Create a docker-compose file/kubernetes for a SETUP a stack on docker containers
   Stack includes: 1. Nginx reverse-proxy
                  2. ReactJS application (https://github.com/Rhymond/product-compare-react)
    Note: Write the docker file also for building reactJS application
